{"tid":2070781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「奶路臣街」以「食字」歧視女性 應改名","createTime":"2020-06-19T10:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T08:07:59.000Z","uid":169112,"like":117,"dislike":217,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"04393c1640c8967efc9dbb4472c779242b95eff9","tid":2070781,"uid":169112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:57:46.000Z","msg":"【數不盡的歧視&mdash;&mdash;細數帶歧視成份的地名#1】<br />\n<br />\n香港充滿了歧視語言，下圖是其中一個例子。Nelson常見的音譯是尼森、尼爾森或納爾遜，但這條街卻故意用「食字」的方式侮辱女性（指要「露」出「奶」子才能做官），歧視程度令人髮指！女性乳房長期被用來嘲笑女性，連「女權1.0」鄭月娥女士都被稱嘲作「奶媽」，其支持者更被嘲為「奶粉」。稍具性別意識的人都明白這條街道的歧視意識何具嚴重，唯在香港政確指出前竟無人聲討，可見香港的性別意識和平等程度還有極大的進步空間。<br />\n<br />\n港府應立即遮蔽這種歧視語言，並全面檢討公共設施中的語言使用！否則小孩子天天受這種思想潛而默化，後果不堪設想！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5PMdB2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5PMdB2c.jpg&h=f96c6245&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n<br />\n政確錄01&mdash;&mdash;「甚麼是政治正確」：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCorrectness/?ref=bookmarks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCorrectness%2F%3Fref%3Dbookmarks&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C0YnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=6ff331fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCorrectness/?ref=bookmarks</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCorrectness/photos/a.1282790118477818/1317366911686805/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCorrectness%2Fphotos%2Fa.1282790118477818%2F1317366911686805%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C0YnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=03973fc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCorrectness/photos/a.1282790118477818/1317366911686805/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"f893d6e15b51aebc543f8e6a581a17103b7ec34c","tid":2070781,"uid":169112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:58:25.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"48e0842adb41906cfbd381b731d0c4233f386419","tid":2070781,"uid":169112,"like":0,"dislik